[
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Li Jinbao.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        李金宝\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Mongols.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        蒙古人\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "They have already destroyed the temple at North Peak.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        他们已经毁了北峰的庙\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "-Where are the nuns? -In the cloisters. East.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        -道姑们呢？\n-在东边的道观\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Remember the oath. We fight to the end.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        记住那句誓言 我们誓死抵抗\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "[Hundred Eyes] Life and death are one thread.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        生死悬于一线\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I will guard the scrolls.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        我来守护经卷\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "[woman] Li Jinbao!\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        李金宝！\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Do not kill him.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        别杀他\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "The Khan will want this one.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        这人可汗肯定要\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "What kind of monk is able to kill, by himself, 25 Mongol soldiers?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        什么样的道士能\n一人杀死25个蒙古士兵？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Is it a form of dark magic practiced at your temple?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你在道观中\n修炼的是邪魔之术？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "You shall never know, shall you?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你永远不会知道 好吗？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "What did you just say, monk?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你说什么 道士？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "You destroyed a temple\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你毁了一座庙\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "and all of the ancient scrolls that contained the answers you seek.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        那些古经卷中藏着你要的答案\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "You monks were offering shelter to my enemies in South China.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你们这些道士\n为我中原南部的敌人提供庇护\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "No place defies the Khan.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        任何地方都不得反抗大汗\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I will ask you again.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        我再问你一遍\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "If you hold your tongue, I will take your tongue.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你要缄默不语的话\n朕就割去你的舌\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "What is this fighting art kept secret in a mountain temple?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        一座山间小庙\n藏了什么武学秘密？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "-The art of peace. -[Kublai chuckles]\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        和平之道\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "You break the necks of trained soldiers,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        朕的士兵都训练有素\n却被你拧断脖颈\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "cut their throats, gut them like wild pigs,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        切断咽喉 掏出内脏\n遭到野猪般的对待\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "and you call it peace?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你说这叫和平？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "You destroy a temple and call it destiny?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你毁了一座庙\n却说那是天命？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Kings of the past would not have shown you grace.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        过去的帝王可不会\n给你这种恩典\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Me, when I make war on a city,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        朕攻破城池后\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I allow the craftsmen to live.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        都不杀工匠\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I conscript them into service... and they live.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        我会征召他们为朕效命\n他们都活着\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Here.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        就在这里\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "You will reveal these Chinese secrets to my war ministers.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你要为朕的军中将领\n揭开汉人的武学秘密\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Reveal Chinese secrets... to fight the Chinese.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        用汉人的武学去攻打汉人\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Prove yourself useful, you can live.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        证明你有用 你就能活\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Defy my laws...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        违抗朕的律法\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "you'll die a death far worse than that suffered by the monks\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你会比那些道士死得惨\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "who perished with your scrolls.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        他们已和你们的经卷一起灭亡\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Oh, you find humor in my decree?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你以为朕的法令是开玩笑吗？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "There is only one Supreme Executioner.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        世上只有一个神\n能主宰别人的命运\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "And those who try to take his place\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        谁要试图谋夺他的位置\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "are like children trying to carve wood as a master carpenter.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        那就是好高骛远\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Most will injure their own hands.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        终会自食苦果\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "You do not fear death?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你不怕死？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I do not cling to life.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        我并非贪生之人\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "There is a difference.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        二者有区别\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Remove him.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        带他下去\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "This wrestler is named Black Steppe Boar.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        这位摔跤手叫\n“黑色草原野猪”\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "A prisoner captured in Scythia.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        是我们在辛西亚的俘虏\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Do you know why he is named after the boar?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        知道他为何要以野猪命名吗？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "His resemblance is extraordinary.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        二者有惊人的相似之处\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "He is called Boar because he has killed such without a weapon many times.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        他叫“野猪”是因为他曾\n多次徒手杀死野猪\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Boar will advance. He will seize you.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        野猪会上前来抓住你\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "You will demonstrate how to break the grasp.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你展示如何破他的招\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "You cover my eyes?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你蒙住我的双眼？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Is that just?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        这公平吗？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "The Great Khan wants a report on how you fight blindfolded.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        大汗想知道蒙住双眼后\n你如何打斗\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "He is a most capricious fool.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        他是最反复无常的傻瓜\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "And if you were not cowards, you would tell him the same.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        若你不是懦夫\n就该对他说同样的话\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "[yelling] Quiet, monk!\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        闭嘴 道士！\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "The general you killed was the son of Subutai.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你杀死的将军是速不台之子\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Do you know that name, monk?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        认识他吗 道士？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I do not.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        不认识\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "[Kublai] Greatest military commander ever to serve Genghis Khan.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        成吉思汗麾下\n最骁勇善战的将领\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "You slayed his son.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你杀了他儿子\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "This is a crime beyond crimes.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        真是罪大恶极\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Yet...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        但是…\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "you do not cling to life, as you say.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        正如你所言 你不贪生\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Death means nothing.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        死对你来说不算什么\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "What is a Khan to do?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        大汗能怎么办？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "A merchant once gifted me a white crane from Lesser Armenia...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        一名商人曾向朕进贡了\n一只小亚美尼亚的白鹤…\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "a water bird that was most uncommon...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        是一种极为罕见的水鸟…\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "because it had been born all black.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        因为这只鸟全身漆黑\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Black white crane.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        黑色的白鹤\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I knew it was an auspicious being that would bring me fortune, but...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        朕知道它是个吉祥物\n能带给朕好运…\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "that black white crane refused to stay on my lake.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        但那只黑色的白鹤\n不肯在朕的湖里停留\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Always, it would fly away.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        它总是飞走\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Just its natural calling, you see.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        那是它的自然天性使之\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "So...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        因此…\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I served him and my fortune...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        朕只好剪掉它一只翅膀…\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "by cutting one wing.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        来留住它和朕的好运\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "[justice minister reading] \"By law of the Grand Khan, Lord of Lords...\"\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        “依大可汗之律法…”\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "[Kublai] Why do you think I had you fight blindfolded?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你以为朕为何要你蒙眼打斗？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Because I'm a capricious fool?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        因为朕是反复无常的傻瓜？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Or to see if you are capable\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        朕是要看看\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "of your Taoist secrets and skills while in the dark?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你能否在黑暗中展示\n道家的秘密武术？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "\"So be it.\"\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        “钦此”\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "[Kublai] Because I knew the moment you were presented,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        因为你被带来的那一刻\n朕就知道\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "you would not be like the obedient painter...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你不会像乖乖就范的画师\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "the resigned astrologer, the noble poet contented with wine.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        听天由命的占星师\n或是有酒就满足的贵族诗人\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "You would refuse to serve the Mongol Empire.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你会拒绝为蒙古帝国效命\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "To this day...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        时至今日\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "that black white crane remains on my lake.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        那只黑色的白鹤仍在朕的湖中\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "He is mine...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        它属于朕\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "and he is beloved.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        深得朕的喜爱\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Are you now ready...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你准备好…\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "to teach my Ministers of Warfare?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        教授朕的军中将领了吗？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Tea for the monk.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        给这道士上茶\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Do not confuse me with one of your holy Buddhists.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        别将我与你心中\n神圣的佛教徒混淆\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Wine.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        上酒\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "You were punished for killing the son of Subutai.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你因杀死速不台之子而受罚\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Never forget that.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        永远不要忘记这点\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I shall not.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        我不会\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "The monks of Wudang spend their lives trying to achieve true emptiness.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        武当道士修炼一生\n只为达到太虚境界\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "For only when the sage can overcome the self\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        圣人只有战胜了自我\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "does he enter into the Tao.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        方能入道\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "That is a dark mystery beyond all mysteries,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        那是超越所有神秘的黑暗秘密\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "and a gift you gave to me.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        是你赐予我的礼物\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Blind?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        盲眼？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I now see the world with one hundred eyes.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        我现在犹如有百眼看世道\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Give him more wine.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        再赐他一杯酒\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I've just captured your horse.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        朕刚刚逮住了你的马\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I know.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        我知道\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Then know this.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        那你要知道\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "There are four Taoist temples still standing in the Wudang Mountains.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        现在武当山上还有四座庙\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "My men will go there in a fortnight and burn them to the ground.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        朕会派人在半月内赶到\n将其夷为平地\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "At my single command,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        朕一声令下\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "your religion can be wiped off the face of this earth.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你信仰的宗教\n就会从这世上消失\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Or it can live...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        或者也能继续存在…\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "grow...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        发展…\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "thrive...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        繁荣…\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "if you prove its value to me.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        只要你向朕证明其价值\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "By training your ministers?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        通过训练你的将领？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "And someone else.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        还有其他人\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "[Hundred Eyes] You must be the prince.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你一定是太子\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I am called Altai.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        我叫阿尔泰\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "[Hundred Eyes] Why are you here?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你为何来此？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "[Altai] Lessons.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        授课\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "And what do you intend to teach me\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        那你打算通过这些…课\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "in these... lessons?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        教我什么？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I'm here to teach you that even the son of a royal khan\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        我来此是要教你\n即便是大汗的儿子\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "is capable of humility and learning.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        也会谦虚 会学习\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Then take the broom, Altai, and sweep my floor.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        那拿起那把扫帚 阿尔泰\n帮我扫扫地\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Good answer. If only you believed it.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        答得好 只要你相信\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "You are a little nomad weed in the garden of the world.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你是天下这个花园中的\n一株小野草\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "They wish you to grow into a flowering tree.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        他们期望你长成\n繁花盛开的大树\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "What is the most important part of such a tree?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        这棵树上最重要的是什么？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "The many branches and the flowering.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        枝繁叶茂 繁花盛开\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I speak of legacy.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        我是说遗产\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Ah! Thank you for untangling your elusive metaphor.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        感谢你解开这个迷人的比喻\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "We begin with roots.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        我们从根基开始\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "[Altai] May I ask a question?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        我能问个问题吗？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Do.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        问吧\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "If you wish calligraphy on your wall,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        若你想在墙上写字\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "why not summon a painter who can see?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        为何不召个明眼的画师？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Can you not read the character I made?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你不认识我写的字？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "It is a symbol for fire.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        像是火字\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Then what is wrong?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        有何不对？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "-It's upside down. -Precisely.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        -颠倒了\n-对\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "This is the kung fu character for patience, control.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        这个字很费功夫\n考验耐心和控制力\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Remember this in the future, always,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        将来都要记住这点\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "\"Never give way to anger.\"\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        “制怒”\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Sifu?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        师傅？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Have I not trained you into exhausted silence yet?\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        我还未把你训练到\n累得说不出话吗？\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Today's lesson is done, My Radiant Highness.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        今日的课业已结束 殿下\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "You cannot see it, I know. But...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        朕知道你看不见\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I assure you it has been overseen by a great Chinese architect...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        但朕可以告诉你\n此地由杰出的汉人建造师监造\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "made from the most precious of woods and hides, and--\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        用最珍贵的木材和兽皮\n还有…\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Imbecile.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        愚蠢\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Someone has painted the character of fire upside down.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        有人把火字倒着写\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I did.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        我写的\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "On this day of the New Year...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        今日新年伊始\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I ordain this place the Hall of the Fourth Treasure.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        朕将此地命名为“四宝殿”\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I name you Hundred Eyes...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        朕为你赐名“百眼”\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "-[chuckles] -...Minister of Martial Affairs.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        封你为武术大臣\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "And so...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        还有…\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I ask of you, as a Wudang priest,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        你是武当道士\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "give my son his Chinese name.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        朕请你为朕的儿子起个汉名\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "There have been 500 over time\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        过去已有500人\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "who have held the name Emperor of All China,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        取了中原帝王之名\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Son of Heaven.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        天子\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Ordained by blood,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        鉴于血统\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "there are those who would have been better suited to harvest cow dung\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        比起统治天下最大的王国\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "than to rule the greatest empire on earth.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        有人则更适合拾牛粪\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "There are those who were as silver,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        有人如银子\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "a lesser metal, but worthy of coinage.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        一种较次的金属\n却有铸币之价值\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "And then there are those...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        还有人…\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "like cold stone,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        如冷漠的石头\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "who force their strength and fury\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        将其力量和愤怒强加于人\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "and win the title by fear and intimidation.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        靠恐吓和威胁取胜\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Blood is nothing.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        血统不值一提\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "Heart and spirit make the sage.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        心胸和精神才能成就圣人\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "And by this...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        故此…\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "I give this boy the name Jingim.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        我为这孩子取名真金\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "\"True gold.\"\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        “真正的金子”\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "So be it.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        如此甚好\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "He will walk out of here with this name,\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        今日起他就叫此名\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "and carry it as his own into a tomorrow only the oracles can see.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        后世也会以此名铭记他\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "As for you, priest...\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        至于你 道士…\n                        \n                    "
    }
  },
  {
    "translation": {
      "en": "this temple is yours.\n\n\n",
      "zh": "\n                        \n                        这座庙是你的了\n                        \n                    "
    }
  }
]